  "aboutInline": {
    "Hor Chanthorn": "何陈通",
    "Khna Ra": "赫纳拉",
    "Our Story Since 2008": "自 2008 年以来我们的故事",
    "More Than a Restaurant": "不仅仅是一家餐厅",
    "Sous Chef": "副主厨",
    "Explore Our Story": "探索我们的故事",
    "Our Story": "我们的故事",
    "Reserve a Table": "预订餐桌",
    "At One More, experience the legacy of Cambodian cuisine through Chef Hor Chanthorn's 15 years of experience, vision, and passion, which shape every dish on our menu. His commitment to preserving and elevating Cambodian cuisine ensures an unparalleled culinary journey for all who dine with us.": "在One More，通过厨师 Hor Chanthorn 15 年的经验、远见和热情体验柬埔寨美食的传统，正是这些经验、远见和热情塑造了我们菜单上的每道菜。他致力于保存和提升柬埔寨美食，确保为所有与我们一起用餐的人提供无与伦比的美食之旅。",
    "At One More, experience the legacy of Cambodian cuisine through Chef Khna Ra's 10 years of experience. His commitment to preserving and elevating Cambodian cuisine ensures an unparalleled culinary journey for all who dine with us.": "在One More，通过厨师 Khna Ra 10 年的经验体验柬埔寨美食的传承。他致力于保存和提升柬埔寨美食，确保为所有与我们一起用餐的人提供无与伦比的美食之旅。",
    "Our Journey": "我们的旅程",
    "Since 2008, One More Restaurant has brought people together through authentic Khmer cuisine, warm hospitality, and memorable celebrations.": "自2008年以来，One More Restaurant通过正宗的高棉美食、热情好客和难忘的庆祝活动将人们聚集在一起。",
    "Our Story Begins": "我们的故事开始了",
    "Expanding Roots": "扩展根源",
    "One More Restaurant begins with a vision to preserve Khmer flavors.": "One More Restaurant始于保留高棉风味的愿景。",
    "Our second home opens, bringing our signature hospitality to a vibrant neighborhood.": "我们的第二个家开业，将我们标志性的热情好客带到了充满活力的社区。",
    "A New Chapter": "新篇章",
    "Today": "今天",
    "Vision and Mission": "愿景与使命",
    "We continue serving families, businesses, and celebrations across Phnom Penh.": "我们继续为金边各地的家庭、企业和庆祝活动提供服务。",
